{
  "id": "69dd4b1f298084f089e574cf",
  "title": "本日の教訓 2026-04-14 suto3",
  "created": 1776110374,
  "updated": 1777300724,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69dd4b1f298084f089e574cf",
      "text": "本日の教訓 2026-04-14 suto3",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776110374,
      "updated": 1776111995
    },
    {
      "id": "69dd517c0000000000eacfb9",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/ec3fd5fe892758c1e71385f436c2dd76]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776111996,
      "updated": 1776111997
    },
    {
      "id": "69dd57fc0000000000e86db5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776113661,
      "updated": 1776113661
    },
    {
      "id": "69dd4b7400000000004883d8",
      "text": "[suto3.icon]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776110453,
      "updated": 1776113661
    },
    {
      "id": "69dd4b7900000000004883d9",
      "text": " 歓迎アイコン[歓迎.icon]更新した",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776110458,
      "updated": 1776110615
    },
    {
      "id": "69dd5ed20000000000e86db6",
      "text": "  黒い文字 + 多色縁取り",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776115410,
      "updated": 1776115449
    },
    {
      "id": "69dd57a00000000000e86db3",
      "text": "  すこしだけ見やすくなったと思う",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776113568,
      "updated": 1776113606
    },
    {
      "id": "69dd5f0b0000000000e86db7",
      "text": "  　ダークテーマで青になったらすこし見づらい",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776115468,
      "updated": 1776115514
    },
    {
      "id": "69dd57d40000000000e86db4",
      "text": "  エフェクトは盛りすぎないように",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776113620,
      "updated": 1776113651
    },
    {
      "id": "69dd627f000000000059613d",
      "text": "  不具合があったので元に戻した",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776116351,
      "updated": 1776116382
    },
    {
      "id": "69dd629e000000000059613e",
      "text": "  [[/suto3/歓迎.icon]] ←開発版",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776116383,
      "updated": 1776116437
    },
    {
      "id": "69dd4ba600000000004883da",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776110502,
      "updated": 1776110511
    },
    {
      "id": "69dd7f930000000000c2d3aa",
      "text": "　[アクティブユーザーの移り変わり。]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776123796,
      "updated": 1776123863
    },
    {
      "id": "69dd7f950000000000c2d3ab",
      "text": "  井戸端のアクティブユーザーは減っているよね",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776123798,
      "updated": 1776123849
    },
    {
      "id": "69dd7fe10000000000c2d3ad",
      "text": "  これ、「。」が居るのか",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776123873,
      "updated": 1776123909
    },
    {
      "id": "69dd7fa00000000000c2d3ac",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776123809,
      "updated": 1776123809
    },
    {
      "id": "69dd8a850000000000c2d3af",
      "text": " 言っていないことが「聞こえてしまう」ひと",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776126598,
      "updated": 1776126647
    },
    {
      "id": "69dd8ab70000000000c2d3b0",
      "text": "  X/Twitter によくいる",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776126647,
      "updated": 1776126668
    },
    {
      "id": "69dd8acc0000000000c2d3b1",
      "text": "  たぶん、井戸端にもいる",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776126668,
      "updated": 1776126691
    },
    {
      "id": "69dd80420000000000c2d3ae",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776123971,
      "updated": 1776123971
    },
    {
      "id": "69dd8ce20000000000c2d3bb",
      "text": "　見えてないものが「見えてしまう」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776127202,
      "updated": 1776127232
    },
    {
      "id": "69dd8ce20000000000c2d3bc",
      "text": "　　私にはこの傾向がある、からあまり他人のことをとやかく言えない",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776127202,
      "updated": 1776127299
    },
    {
      "id": "69dd8d430000000000c2d3be",
      "text": "　　周りからしたら、きっとアブナイひとに見える",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776127299,
      "updated": 1776127333
    },
    {
      "id": "69dd8d020000000000c2d3bd",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776127234,
      "updated": 1776127234
    },
    {
      "id": "69dd8afb0000000000c2d3b2",
      "text": "　行間読み",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776126716,
      "updated": 1776126783
    },
    {
      "id": "69dd8b060000000000c2d3b4",
      "text": "　　しないほうがいいとよく言われるができないと困る",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776126727,
      "updated": 1776126762
    },
    {
      "id": "69dd8b400000000000c2d3b6",
      "text": "　　[行間を読み取って解釈した文章にツッコミ]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776126784,
      "updated": 1776126800
    },
    {
      "id": "69dd8b600000000000c2d3b7",
      "text": "　　 あ、[空リンク]だ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776126816,
      "updated": 1776126841
    },
    {
      "id": "69dd8b790000000000c2d3b8",
      "text": "　　 こんなふうに、有用そうに見えて内容のないリンクを見つけるとへこむ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776126842,
      "updated": 1776126954
    },
    {
      "id": "69dd8bf10000000000c2d3b9",
      "text": "　　 　内容のないリンク = 空リンク でそれ以外の含意はない",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776126962,
      "updated": 1776127132
    },
    {
      "id": "69dd8d830000000000c2d3bf",
      "text": "　　 　私の文章はこういうスタイル",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776127363,
      "updated": 1776127386
    },
    {
      "id": "69dd8c2f0000000000c2d3ba",
      "text": "　　 [suto3.icon]は 10のダメージをうけた!!",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776127023,
      "updated": 1776127063
    },
    {
      "id": "69dd8e5e0000000000c2d3c0",
      "text": "　　[妖怪行間読め]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776127582,
      "updated": 1776127594
    },
    {
      "id": "69dd8e780000000000c2d3c1",
      "text": "　　 これも空リンク",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776127608,
      "updated": 1776127624
    },
    {
      "id": "69dd8b070000000000c2d3b5",
      "text": "　　 [suto3.icon]は 8のダメージをうけた!!",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776126727,
      "updated": 1776127645
    },
    {
      "id": "69dd8afb0000000000c2d3b3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776126716,
      "updated": 1776126716
    },
    {
      "id": "69dd94910000000000c2d3c7",
      "text": "　[大喜利]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776129169,
      "updated": 1776129184
    },
    {
      "id": "69dd953f0000000000e179bd",
      "text": "　 最近、大喜利やってないな",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776129343,
      "updated": 1776129369
    },
    {
      "id": "69de0a0200000000007c8d0d",
      "text": "　 やってみる",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776159234,
      "updated": 1776159240
    },
    {
      "id": "69dd97e70000000000c2d3d3",
      "text": "　　 [こんなふーこはイヤだ]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776130024,
      "updated": 1776159246
    },
    {
      "id": "69dd94980000000000c2d3c8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776129176,
      "updated": 1776129179
    },
    {
      "id": "69ddbae50000000000c772e3",
      "text": " [心理学の三大巨頭]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776138981,
      "updated": 1776138991
    },
    {
      "id": "69ddbae90000000000c772e4",
      "text": "  [バカっぽいのが気に入って載せた]のに、真面目な話をしている…",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1776138985,
      "updated": 1777300724
    },
    {
      "id": "69ddbcfb00000000008597f6",
      "text": "  誠に申し訳ございません[terang.icon]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776139516,
      "updated": 1776141802
    },
    {
      "id": "69ddc5ee00000000003dbae2",
      "text": "  　謝る必要はないんですけど [suto3.icon]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776141807,
      "updated": 1776141842
    },
    {
      "id": "69ddc61a00000000003dbae3",
      "text": "  　そういうネタだとわかってもらえなかったと困惑している ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776141851,
      "updated": 1776141911
    },
    {
      "id": "69de0c9100000000007c8d0e",
      "text": "  　　そして、文章を消してしまった。もったいない",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776159889,
      "updated": 1776159920
    },
    {
      "id": "69ddca850000000000dbdba4",
      "text": "  「三大なんとか」という表現が好きなの日本と韓国だけだという印象がある",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776142982,
      "updated": 1776143068
    },
    {
      "id": "69ddce690000000000c772e6",
      "text": "  「心理学の巨人」というネタを思いついた",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776143977,
      "updated": 1776144017
    },
    {
      "id": "69ddce950000000000c772e7",
      "text": "  　行動主義の巨人  : バラス・スキナー",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776144022,
      "updated": 1776144115
    },
    {
      "id": "69ddcef40000000000dbdba5",
      "text": "  　発達心理学の巨人 : ジャン・ピアジェ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776144116,
      "updated": 1776144182
    },
    {
      "id": "69ddcf370000000000dbdba6",
      "text": "  　など",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776144183,
      "updated": 1776144187
    },
    {
      "id": "69ddcf3d0000000000dbdba7",
      "text": "  　ネタなので真面目に考えてはいない",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776144190,
      "updated": 1776144219
    },
    {
      "id": "69ddd2970000000000dbdbab",
      "text": "  　[https://www.gaigo.co.jp/dvd/GLE-041_GIANTS_OF_PSYCHOLOGY.html 心理学の巨人たち / GIANTS OF PSYCHOLOGY - 日本外語協会]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776145048,
      "updated": 1776145053
    },
    {
      "id": "69ddd2a20000000000dbdbac",
      "text": "  　 こんなシリーズがあるのか",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776145058,
      "updated": 1776145079
    },
    {
      "id": "69ddd2c30000000000dbdbad",
      "text": "  　 心理学の巨人たちで打線が組めそう",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776145092,
      "updated": 1776145111
    },
    {
      "id": "69de03f200000000007c8ce5",
      "text": "  　 [心理学の巨人軍で打線を組んだ]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776157683,
      "updated": 1776157689
    },
    {
      "id": "69de092b00000000007c8d0c",
      "text": "  　 できてしまった（自分でも驚いている）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776159019,
      "updated": 1776159047
    },
    {
      "id": "69ddbaf20000000000c772e5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776138994,
      "updated": 1776138994
    },
    {
